title: The Mikado 1939
description:
Some time ago I uploaded the 1984 Canadian production of the Mikado with subtitles 

written by me. Since then I have come across excerpts of the 1939 production with 

Kenny Baker. I was impressed but discouraged by the difficulty obtaining a copy. It 

took considerable time to download the large ISO file. Determined to make it more

available I am uploading this version. It was only after finishing did I notice that

the general opinion of it was no too favorable as you can read by my inclosed text

file from IMBd.
